            <text xml:id="ed_rubens_277_lat">
                <body>
                    <div part="Y" xml:lang="lat">
                        <p><pb n="143"/>D. O. M. S.<lb/>
                            <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#pypelincx_maria">MARIAE PEPELINGIAE</rs>
                            prudentiss.<lb/> lectiss. faeminae, quae matrimonio iuncta<lb/> fuit <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_jan">IOANNI RUBENIO</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Jan</term>
                            </index> I. C. &amp; Senatori<lb/>
                            <pb n="144"/><lb/>
                            <rs type="place" ref="../register/register-place.xml#antwerpen">Antverpiensi</rs>, eoque orbata
                            viduitatem<lb/> ad diem fari per annos XXII. religiose co<lb/>luit, <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_philipp">Philippus</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Philipp</term>
                            </index> &amp; <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_peter_paul">Petrus
                                Paullus Rubenij</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Peter Paul</term>
                            </index><lb/> cum nepotibus e filia <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_blandina">Blandina</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term xml:lang="deu">Rubens, Blandina</term>
                            </index>, piae matri<lb/> &amp; B. M. F. Vixit annos LXX. <date when="1533">M. VI. D. XXIX.</date><lb/> Obijt <date when="1608-10-19">XIV. kal. Novemb. A. M. DCVIII</date>.<lb/>
                        </p>
                        <p rend="text-align:center">Ibidem.<lb/> MATRI-VIRGINI,<lb/> hanc tabulam à
                            se pictam,<lb/> de suo ornatam,<lb/> pio affectu ad opt. matris
                            sepulcrum<lb/> commune cum uxore <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#brant_isabella">ISABELLA BRANT</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Brant, Isabella</term>
                            </index><lb/> sua sibi die PETRUS PAULUS RUBENS<lb/> L. M. D.<lb/> Ipso
                            D. MICHAELIS Archangeli,<lb/> Anno <date when="1610">M. D.
                            CX.</date><lb/> PHILIPPO RUBENIO I.C.<lb/> Ioannis ciuis &amp;
                            Senatoris Antverp. F.<lb/> magni <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#lipsius_justus">LIPSI</rs><index indexName="psw">
                                <term type="PND" xml:lang="deu">Lipsius, Justus</term>
                            </index> discipulo &amp; alumno,<lb/> cuius doctrinam poenè
                            assecutus,<lb/> modestiam feliciter adaequavit:<lb/>
                            <rs type="place" ref="../register/register-place.xml#bruessel">Bruxellae</rs> Praesidi <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#richardot">RICHARDOTO</rs>;<lb/>
                            <rs type="place" ref="../register/register-place.xml#rom">Romae</rs>
                            <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#colonna_ascanio">ASCANIO Cardinali
                            COLUMNAE</rs>.<lb/> ab epistolis &amp; studiis,<lb/> S. P. Q.
                            Antverpiensis à secretis.<lb/> Abiit non obiit, virtute &amp;
                            scriptis sibi su<lb/>perstes,<lb/>
                            <date when="1611-08-28">v. kal. Sep. an. Ch.
                                CIƆ.IƆCXI </date>aet. XXXIIXX.<lb/> Marito
                            benemerenti <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#moy_maria">MARIA DE MOII</rs>,<lb/>
                            duum ex illo liberorum <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_clara">Clarae</rs>, &amp; <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_philippus">Philip<lb/>pi</rs> mater,<lb/>
                            <lb/>
                            <pb n="145"/>propter illius eiusque matris MARIAE PII<lb/>PELINCK
                            sepulcrum<lb/> hoc moeroris &amp; amoris sui monumentum P. C.<lb/>
                            Bonu, Viator, bene precare manibus:<lb/> Et cogita; praivit ille mox
                            sequar.</p>
                    </div>
